Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:09.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! We need to be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don’t look! If you see their eyes,\N you won’t be able to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:15.42,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Wounds and Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alti, let’s follow\Nthose birds! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re in the middle\Nof a mission right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not like the enemy’s around, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re only out here\Nbecause they’re paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:39.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ve been flying for\Na long time, haven’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far they’re going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not like they’ve been\Nflying the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,They rest their wings\Nwhen they get tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,and they have to eat sometime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,What on earth are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re in the middle of a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:12.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone’s\Nbeen really distracted lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though we finally managed to get put back on duty, everyone’s still a little out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:22.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even Aaeru isn’t flying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:25.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,How’s the Sibylla Aurea\Nbeen doing lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The same, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don’t like the feeling of being somehow incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:44.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I’m starting to get used\Nto the others being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:51.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess we can’t go back to being the old Chor Tempest after all, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, I’ve only ever\Nhad my eyes on you, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come along, Limone.\NWe’re going to the pool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:12.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re still small, so you need to build up your stamina—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You come back here this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we all sit down\Nand eat together first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong,\NSibylla Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t this… the Sibylla Aurea’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s still being repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve had to rebuild her\Nalmost from the ground up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,and it’s been hard to get\Nall the parts we’ve needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your wounds still\Nhaven’t healed, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s been a long time\Nsince you’ve flown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Hey, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:28.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Instead of hiding in there all the time, pull yourself together and get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you haven’t come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest only gets sent\Non pointless missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:41.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we can’t fly\Nif we’re stuck in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, that pig-headed…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I swear, what a childish thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose I’m in no position to talk…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:45.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,You really didn’t need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, it’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, Aaeru is such a troublesome girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,She must be getting on your nerves.\N Should I make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, that might\Nrequire drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t you think it’s time\Nyou made a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whatever you’re going to do. Things can’t go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you going to come\Nback to the choir or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you intend to go to the Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,then this time, I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:38.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether to go to the Spring, or to keep flying the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still can’t decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I realize I have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:51.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… whichever choice I make, it feels like it will be a betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,A betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s the feeling I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of Amuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:15.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have been at your side\Never since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:17.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve walked beside you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is why I can tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,you are meant to fly a Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:31.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,even if that means betraying Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t talk about it\Nlike you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that’s how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,She just doesn’t give an inch, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though you’ve been\Nso worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why doesn’t she try\Nto understand how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:30.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t stand Neviril\Nwhen she’s like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t talk about her\Nlike you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t she basically just\Nacting like a spoiled child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:56.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know losing Amuria\Nhas been hard for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,but she’s not the only one\Nwho misses her, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shutting herself away like that is just a big pain for everyone around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry. I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just doing a little cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can’t just leave them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know! Wait a minute, okay?{\NI’ll be right back.}{Pulling out of your ass a whole sentence, seriously?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like\Nthey’re starting to sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since you have such beautiful nails, you have to take good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium-sama\Nwill scold you if you don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You look like you’re having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s because I can do something\Nto help you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I get to touch you while I do it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think… she’s probably lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone on board…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is probably lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does my face give it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s just that… I’m lonely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,My, isn’t it hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then shall we go someplace cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:13.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still no change from our princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, this certainly\Nbrings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does she remind you of anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:28.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s hardly uncommon for a sibylla to have doubts about flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:34.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I reached out to you\Nback then, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven’t forgotten.
Comment: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Zooooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da! Zoooom!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:45.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Zooooom! KABOOM! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still more of you coming?
Comment: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Zoooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmpf! I’m not afraid\Nof an attack like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you think you can hit us,\N go ahead and try!
Comment: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Zoooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, Para-sama! Enemy to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fire the machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Comment: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re incredible, Para-sama!\NNot a single miss!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da!  Da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here come more of them,\Nthrough the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stingray Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:30.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s do a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We do this all the time, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we have to shut it off, or…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu-nee-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I decided I’d stay with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:17.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being with her seemed like the most natural thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one\Nwho could take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:54.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t the only one\Nwho was hurt back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:59.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe that’s why…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you’re still a child, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I’m not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s why, when we try\Nto heal each other’s wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,we just end up inflicting more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:34.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m leaving now. Good night, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why can’t you understand, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:15.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That does it. Stubborn or not, \NI’m going to drag you out myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I get the feeling that talking isn’t what you had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Maaju Pool can\Nalso be used for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, why do I have to do this with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:06.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria isn’t the only reason \NNeviril is refusing to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was thinking about me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But at least let me tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven’t ever felt\Nthat you betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m grateful that\Nyou worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:48.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I’ll entrust you to someone who could be\N even better for you than Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:02.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:13.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, you have to become Neviril’s pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t need to tell {\i1}me{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose\Nhappens to them after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Birds that rest their wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:05.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said they couldn’t\Nkeep flying forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ll start flying again, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:14.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Flying through the sky is what they’re born to do, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What they’re born to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:23.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they’re just resting\Ntheir wings, then that’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:30.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But a bird that’s too badly hurt to fly…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:33.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,…won’t be able to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:06.67,Titles,,85,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,In order to sign a ceasefire agreement,\NHighlander diplomats come aboard the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:18.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over International Waters
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Over International Waters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:09.75,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:20.38,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I’ve made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.50,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:06.98,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:14.28,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:20.99,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair… Don’t you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:28.18,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:47.94,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds…\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:52.18,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.25,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon’t be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:06.95,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart’s overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:19.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,“I want to get closer to you.”\N“I want to feel your pulse.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:24.91,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:28.92,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:32.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart’s desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can’t reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:44.34,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:53.44,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:59.56,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to “now” the way it is…
